OL,3,CGardai pass new Creeslough
OL,4,Cinvestigation file to prosecutors
OL,6,FGardai investigating the Creeslough
OL,7,Fexplosion have confirmed that a new
OL,8,Ffile has been submitted to the
OL,9,FRepublic's Director of Public
OL,10,FProsecutions.
OL,12,FThis supplementary file is in addition
OL,13,Fto the primary file which was
OL,14,Fsubmitted last September. Ten people
OL,15,Fwere killed in an explosion at a
OL,16,Fpetrol station in the Donegal village
OL,17,Fin October 2022.
OL,19,FThe blast claimed the lives of four
OL,20,Fmen, three women and three children
OL,21,Faged between 5 and 59.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
