OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775239864
OL,3,CGardai pass new Creeslough
OL,4,Cinvestigation file to prosecutors
OL,6,FIt's suspected that a gas leak led to
OL,7,Fthe explosion which destroyed a shop
OL,8,Fand an apartment block. Seven people
OL,9,Fwere arrested and questioned as part
OL,10,Fof a criminal investigation into the
OL,11,Ftragedy.
OL,13,FThe new file sent to DPP includes
OL,14,Fformal recommendations from Gardai.
OL,15,FIt's understood it's now up to the DPP
OL,16,Foffice to decide if those arrested
OL,17,Fshould face charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
