OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775239864
OL,3,CGardai pass new Creeslough
OL,4,Cinvestigation file to prosecutors
OL,6,FVictims' families were informed of the
OL,7,Flatest development at a meeting on
OL,8,FThursday. Gardai say families continue
OL,9,Fto be supported by their family
OL,10,Fliaison officers.
OL,12,FAn appeal has also been made for
OL,13,Fanyone with any information in
OL,14,Frelation to the fatal explosion who is
OL,15,Fstill to come forward to speak to the
OL,16,FGarda Investigation team.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
